{"id": 1258, "genre": 1001, "title": "你最无法忍受哪些乘飞机的糟糕体验？", "description": "好奇心研究所不定期会推出当季应景并充满正义感的“无！法！忍！受！”小调查，欢迎来表态。（题图来自：Emiliano Ponzi）", "record_count": 6763, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201610081734148ivVG7DX24jqQbJs.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-11-23T03:00:32Z", "options": [{"id": 136192, "content": "九元的行李托运和爆炸的空姐推销", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147614}, {"id": 136448, "content": "坐我后面一个小孩腿短放不到地上，就一直踢我座椅。不是脚顶着座椅，而是一直踢我！跟家长也说了，家长管不了她，一说她就尖叫然后再更密集踢我、好像深井冰发作一样！被踢了一路真是要疯", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 841943}, {"id": 136193, "content": "难道没人觉得是：登机时候有人放行李挡路吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 480284}, {"id": 136450, "content": "每次停止使用卫生间都没有时间提醒，都是仓促的说现在停止使用洗手间。what？？！！就不能用了？不会提早说几分钟后就不能使用了吗？？", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 615579}, {"id": 136451, "content": "食物", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 795957}, {"id": 136196, "content": "睡觉呼噜噜", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 843652}, {"id": 136452, "content": "要关手机体验差，美国坐飞机无须关手机关电脑", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 811204}, {"id": 136197, "content": "卫生间脏", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 820321}, {"id": 136453, "content": "前后左右坐小孩 情侣要坐一起看你一个人又小 让你让座位", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 738781}, {"id": 171269, "content": "飞机一停稳就抢着拿行李.然后sb一样站在过道中。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 948209}, {"id": 136198, "content": "1.长时间保持一个姿势，睡觉腿伸不开\n2.空姐态度差\n3.下飞机迟迟不开仓门", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 724521}, {"id": 136454, "content": "春秋航空的空中售卖吵死了，一趟买不了几个，为了这点钱损害全机顾客体验，不知道春秋在想啥，廉价航空这样做也是弊大于利", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 811204}, {"id": 136199, "content": "耳鸣到崩溃！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 843670}, {"id": 136455, "content": "同机的Bastard.", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 743246}, {"id": 136200, "content": "外国和港澳台的空姐们对中国老人的不文明行径相视一眼 无可奈何的时候.让我觉得自己国家的文明素质真的很糟糕", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 706063}, {"id": 136456, "content": "不关手机竟然还听歌", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 844618}, {"id": 136457, "content": "中国联合航空的最恶心，啥都要钱，行李，食物，水。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 804573}, {"id": 136202, "content": "各种延迟?", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 720017}, {"id": 136458, "content": "飞机的座位除头等舱外都显得太小气了……", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1119601}, {"id": 136970, "content": "邻座一直关注着你的一举一动，空姐服务态度冷淡", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 846770}, {"id": 136203, "content": "抢着登机 又不是没位子，上机后抢行李架，堵在中间让后面的人过不去…", "image": null, "praise_count": 43, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 396158}, {"id": 136459, "content": "脱鞋", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 328369}, {"id": 136204, "content": "看了一眼就想摔回给乘务员的东航飞机餐", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 2007}, {"id": 136460, "content": "一些大妈说话声音太响。特别是在春秋航空上特别明显。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 836783}, {"id": 136205, "content": "吵闹的熊孩子，吵闹的熊家长", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 799001}, {"id": 136461, "content": "一直吵个不停", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 311434}, {"id": 137485, "content": "熊孩子\n还有狐臭?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 848613}, {"id": 136206, "content": "周围有人各种呼噜", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 835506}, {"id": 136207, "content": "东西不好吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 148298}, {"id": 136208, "content": "一直搞不懂手机为什么要有飞行模式？", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 798219}, {"id": 136209, "content": "穿着黑丝短裙在我身边晃来晃去的，不经意的时候用翘臀碰到我。", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 601736}, {"id": 136465, "content": "前面的把椅背调得很低，影响我看书学习……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 820245}, {"id": 136210, "content": "有的装逼商务客老早换好登机牌选了靠窗或靠走道位置，遇上带小孩的想换一下座不答应，丫就觉得飞机位置好重要…", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 842788}, {"id": 136466, "content": "座椅靠背顶部朝前弯曲。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 844668}, {"id": 136211, "content": "都还好，就是窗户打不开", "image": null, "praise_count": 40, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 744874}, {"id": 136212, "content": "流量控制", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 843080}, {"id": 136213, "content": "邻座的两位大聊特聊互联网创业形式", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 419781}, {"id": 136214, "content": "航空超售，轮到我没座位了，被迫留了一晚", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 43355}, {"id": 136470, "content": "最烦在飞机上遇到熊孩子了，大吵大闹不说，有次遇到一个后排的把脚抬上来伸老长伸到我扶手上了。怒！大吼一声：“把脚拿下去！”家长也不管管，真是的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 595084}, {"id": 136215, "content": "除了硬件条件让人无法选择之外，大部分的不好体验的缘由还真是全民素质和教养问题", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 843727}, {"id": 192279, "content": "前面那位椅背调地特别靠后", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 958755}, {"id": 136216, "content": "总觉得1-2个小时去机场，1-2个小时在机场等（还没算延误/取消），1-2个小时落地后取行李，1-2个小时从机场去目的地，感觉生命都浪费了...", "image": null, "praise_count": 259, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 521972}, {"id": 136472, "content": "厦航空姐好看，东西好吃！棒！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 654511}, {"id": 136217, "content": "关了手机等待起飞，然后被告知延误起飞，然后打开手机，然后再关上手机等待起飞。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 680556}, {"id": 136729, "content": "没有充电口。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 788952}, {"id": 138265, "content": "熊孩子", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 766293}, {"id": 137500, "content": "1.小朋友要和你换座位，嚷嚷着要靠窗看风景…2.飞机上居然推销产品…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 178202}, {"id": 136221, "content": "撩空姐！", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 791181}, {"id": 206881, "content": "讨厌熊孩子，总是有想要为他吃一粒安眠药的冲动", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1039157}, {"id": 136229, "content": "后面的人总是踢座椅", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 839117}]}